It's Wolfie's birthday. Come on.

00:28:25.790 --> 00:28:27.667
- Two minutes!
- OK.

00:28:27.698 --> 00:28:29.596
- Wolfie!
- Yeah, sweetheart?

00:28:29.627 --> 00:28:31.796
- Who was the guy in the car?
- I don't know what you're talking about.

00:28:32.578 --> 00:28:33.693
- Hey, Ally.
- How's it goin'?

00:28:33.725 --> 00:28:35.800
- Happy birthday.
- "Happy birthday"?

00:28:36.582 --> 00:28:37.687
- Yeah.
- It's not my birthday.

00:28:37.718 --> 00:28:39.804
- What do you mean? Come on.
- No, I was just saying...

00:28:40.585 --> 00:28:42.754
What the hell happened in here?
My God!

00:28:42.786 --> 00:28:45.798
- This place is a mess!
- "Starting gate" is "shuppatsu geto",

00:28:46.580 --> 00:28:49.688
- and "bad beat" is "warui bito".
- What's going on? Leave the butter out?

00:28:49.719 --> 00:28:52.732
Who the hell's betting on horses
at breakfast time in Japan?

00:28:52.763 --> 00:28:54.703
- It's not breakfast time.
- They're loading!

00:28:54.734 --> 00:28:55.798
- Joe, come on!
- You're crazy!

00:28:56.580 --> 00:28:57.779
Have a sizable investment on this.

00:28:57.810 --> 00:28:59.802
What did I say
about smoking in this house?

00:29:00.583 --> 00:29:01.752
- Outside!
- Who are you?

00:29:01.783 --> 00:29:03.764
- It's my house.
- I know it's your house.

00:29:03.795 --> 00:29:06.620
- But you smoke too.
- All right, forget it.

00:29:06.651 --> 00:29:09.623
Sweetheart, you're happy here,
aren't you?

00:29:09.654 --> 00:29:10.676
I'm happy, Dad.

00:29:10.708 --> 00:29:12.803
I'm just saying, she's got no space.

00:29:12.835 --> 00:29:14.691
- What are you saying?
- Sweetheart.

00:29:14.722 --> 00:29:15.838
- She's got no space.
- Wait a minute.

00:29:16.620 --> 00:29:18.726
I want my friends to look at you.

00:29:18.757 --> 00:29:20.759
Take a good look.

00:29:20.790 --> 00:29:24.637
With a voice like from heaven,
but you know what?

00:29:27.651 --> 00:29:29.684
It's not always the best singers
that make it.

00:29:30.622 --> 00:29:35.784
You know? I knew a couple of guys
could sing Sinatra under the table.

00:29:35.815 --> 00:29:38.735
But Frank, he'd come on stage
with the blue eyes,

00:29:38.766 --> 00:29:42.644
the sharkskin suit,
the patent leather shoes...

00:29:42.675 --> 00:29:43.854
he becomes Frank Sinatra.

00:29:44.855 --> 00:29:48.775
And everybody else,
all these other guys...

00:29:48.806 --> 00:29:52.664
that really got it,
that really have it inside...

00:29:53.759 --> 00:29:55.719
..just a bunch of nobodies.

00:29:56.762 --> 00:29:58.879
OK. Everybody, let's go.

00:29:59.661 --> 00:30:00.714
Time for work.

