00:30:27.812 --> 00:30:29.699
- Yeah.
- I'm gonna talk to Bobby

00:30:29.730 --> 00:30:31.732
- and get something set up.
- Sold. I'm sold.

00:30:31.764 --> 00:30:33.745
- All right, Jack.
