00:32:20.920 --> 00:32:23.923
Listen. Does he know you sing at all?
Did he hear anything from you?

00:32:23.954 --> 00:32:26.852
- I gotta go to work.
- It's the opportunity of a lifetime.

00:32:26.883 --> 00:32:28.823
