00:34:12.275 --> 00:34:14.109
Oh, shit!

00:34:17.185 --> 00:34:18.291
I could get used to this shit.

00:34:19.073 --> 00:34:21.200
You need to date more rock stars,
baby girl, you know?

00:34:21.231 --> 00:34:22.295
We're not dating.

